4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT ESTABLISHING SHARED SOLAR AND UTILITY
5 REQUIREMENTS; PROVIDING FOR TRANSMISSION OR DISTRIBUTION INTERCONNECTION FOR
6 SHARED SOLAR ENERGY FACILITIES; DISTINGUISHING SHARED SOLAR CUSTOMERS FROM NET
7 METERING CUSTOMERS; PROVIDING RULEMAKING AUTHORITY; PROVIDING DEFINITIONS; AND
8 PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE EFFECTIVE DATE.”
9
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
11
12 NEW SECTION. Section 1. Short title. [Sections 1 through 6] may be cited as the "Montana Solar
13 Shares Act".
14
15 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Definitions. As used in [sections 1 through 6], unless the context clearly
16 indicates otherwise, the following definitions apply:
