13 public utility, at the request of the subscribing customer, shall transfer the on-bill credit to a new eligible
14 subscribing customer.
15 (7) A subscribing customer may choose to assign their proportion of generated electricity to a
16 nonprofit or a public utility's low-income energy share program.
